  "titleCh": "請假單",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "請假信。Kakeng老師：您好！Butul昨天晚上應該是吃到過期的食物，所以他肚子痛、發燒、腹瀉，還嘔吐到睡不好覺。醫師囑咐需要在家休息，觀察一天，所以今天無法到學校上課，擬向學校請假一天。",
      "ab": "sapihibang ni Butul a cudad. Kakeng saydan, mahica tu! nasandeb caay kakapah ku nikan ni Butul, hakay makaen ku angliway tu a kakanen, kyu adada ku bili, masulalis, mabanic ciniza, salabi nasandeb muuta’ caay kaala ku kakabi’en, kailuma’ henay mihibang sa ku misaydan, azihen henay tu cacay a demiad ku uzip sa, kyu caay katayza i cacudadan ayza tu cacay a demiad. misulit tu sapatudud a cudada i cacudadan tu sapihibang.",
      "order": "1",
